document.title: Woordenboek van de Gelderse Dialecten
document.intro: The Dictionary of the dialects of Gelderland describes specific parts of the general vocabulary. The dictionary has been written around a certain theme. Unlike other local dictionaries that have been published in our province, the vocabulary has been arranged thematically rather than al... Rivierengebied Veluwe
